New module ao_kernel/i18n.py:
- msg(key, **kwargs): localized message lookup
- Resolution: AO_KERNEL_LANG > LC_ALL > LC_MESSAGES > LANG > "en"
- 2 locales: en (default), tr (Turkish)
- 6 message keys: workspace_created, already_exists, errors, mcp, usage

CLI files updated: init_cmd, migrate_cmd, cli.py — all use i18n.msg()
Command names, flags, JSON keys remain English always.

Design decision (Codex CNS-20260413-011):
- English-first for open source (PyPI)
- AO_KERNEL_LANG=tr for Turkish users
- Only user-facing messages localized

10 new tests (priority, fallback, env var override), 271 total passing.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
